And when you lean slightly forward towards the person that's talking to you, you don't need to lean

43
00:03:35.310 --> 00:03:38.220
all the way like this, but just a little forward.

44
00:03:38.730 --> 00:03:43.290
That tells the interviewer that you are invested in that conversation.

45
00:03:44.260 --> 00:03:48.310
